'''飓风亨利'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Henri}}）是[[1979年大西洋飓风季|1979年大西洋飓风季]]第八场获命名的风暴和第五场飓风，也是20世纪第二个进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]但却没有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，这种情况在20世纪一共只发生过四次<ref name="mwr">{{cite web | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1979.pdf | title = 1979 Monthly Weather Review | accessdate = 2017-01-26 | last = Herbert | first = Paul | date = 1980-03-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230202/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1979.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-03-03}}</ref>。系统于9月14日在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西北部成型，風暴在其持續過程中，大部分時間都沒有固定移動方向，僅在起初大致保持了西行的軌跡。9月16日，气旋达到热带风暴强度，并在次日成为飓风。两天后，亨利因外界环境不利而减弱成热带低气压并转向东北，于9月24日同墨西哥湾东北部的[[锋_(气象)|锋面]]低气压区融合。由於风暴移动的速度缓慢且方向難以預測，墨西哥沿海部分地区的居民被迫疏散。儘管气旋在之後減弱，其於[[佛羅里達狹地|佛羅里達狹地]]一帶的降雨依然引發洪災。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Henri 1979 track.png}}
飓风亨利源自离开非洲西岸进入大西洋、于9月14日抵达[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]最西北角的东风波<ref name="tcr1">{{cite web | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211721/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1979-prelim/henri/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1979-prelim/henri/prelim01.gif | title = Hurricane Henri Tropical Cyclone Report - Page 1 | accessdate = 2017-01-27 | last = Hebert | first = Paul J. | year = 1979 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[GIF|GIF]]}}</ref>。经[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机确认，系统当天发展成第十八号热带低气压<ref name="ats">{{cite web | url = http://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/pdf/10.1175/1520-0493(1980)108%3C0966:ATSO%3E2.0.CO;2 | title = Atlantic Tropical Systems of 1979 | accessdate = 2017-01-27 | last = Frank | first = Neil | year = 1980 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | format = PDF | archive-date = 2020-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200522212449/https://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/pdf/10.1175/1520-0493(1980)108%3C0966:ATSO%3E2.0.CO;2 }}</ref>。气旋向北移动掠过[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]东部，进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]后因[[高压脊|高压脊]]阻挡无法继续北上而大幅向西转向，接下来又转朝西南移动，于9月16日升级成热带风暴并获名“亨利”（{{lang|en|Henri}}）<ref name="tcr1"/>。

风暴在途经[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]期间继续强化，在北侧高压脊减弱后于9月17日转向西北，且当天就达到飓风标准，还于六小时后在[[韦拉克鲁斯_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|韦拉克鲁斯]]东北方向约245公里海域达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]140公里的最高强度。接下来墨西哥湾西部上空发展出大规模[[低气压|低气压区]]，导致亨利的动向变得飘忽不定。9月18日，气旋因同陆地相互影响、且[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]近海有[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]逐渐发展带走湿气的共同影响开始稳步减弱。<ref name="tcr1" />9月19日，亨利转向东面移动并降级成热带低气压，然后就再也没有显著再生并转向东北朝大范围[[冷锋|冷锋]]逼近。9月24日，气旋同墨西哥湾东北部的[[低压槽|锋面槽]]融合。<ref name="tcr2">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192502/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1979-prelim/henri/prelim02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1979-prelim/henri/prelim02.gif | title = Hurricane Henri Tropical Cyclone Report - Page 2 | accessdate = 2017-01-27 | last = Hebert | first = Paul J. | year = 1979 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-03-03}}</ref>

飓风亨利是20世纪第二个进入墨西哥湾但却没有登陆的热带气旋，这种情况在整个20世纪也只出现过四次<ref name="mwr" />，另外三次分别是1969年的[[1969年大西洋飓风季#飓风劳瑞|飓风劳瑞]]、1980年的[[1980年飓风珍妮|飓风珍妮]]和1982年的[[1982年飓风阿尔贝托|飓风阿尔贝托]]<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1982 | title = Hurricane Alberto Preliminary Report | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183316/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/alberto/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1982-prelim/alberto/prelim01.gif | accessdate = 2016-05-12 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | location = Miami, FL}}</ref><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]]}}</ref>。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Henri_1979_rainfall.gif|thumb]]

虽然亨利没有登陆，但风暴发展期间还是对[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]西部沿海[[墨西哥行政区划|多个州]]构成威胁<ref name="tcr2" />。墨西哥气象机构向包括[[塔毛利帕斯州|塔毛利帕斯州]][[坦皮科|坦皮科]]、[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]][[图斯潘_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|图斯潘]]和[[瑙特拉_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|瑙特拉]]（{{lang|en|Nautla}}）在内的沿海城镇发布公告，建议居民转移到地势更高的区域<ref name="tyrone1">{{cite news | title = Henri About to Slam into Mexican Port | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press Inc.]] | date = 1979-09-18 | newspaper = Tyrone Daily Herald}}</ref>。韦拉克鲁斯州政府通过广播和电视向可能发生洪灾的沿海地区发布警告<ref name="titusville1">{{cite news | title = Henri Nears Mexico | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | date = 1979-09-18 | publisher = Titusville Herald}}</ref>。

风暴对[[1979年坎佩切湾漏油事故|1979年坎佩切湾漏油事故]]的善后清理工作构成不利影响，专为此次清理工作设计的一个310吨钢质容器受损<ref name="Ixtoc I">{{cite news |last=Mohr |first=Holbrook |title=Oil complicates forecasts on hurricane season eve |url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5j4d8XkzfNJMVGDSkCL64avnjGMHAD9G195800 |accessdate=2010-05-31 |agency=Associated Press |date=2010-05-31 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5q7smRWLe?url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5j4d8XkzfNJMVGDSkCL64avnjGMHAD9G195800 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2010-05-31 }}</ref>。亨利在[[卡门城|卡门城]]产生狂风暴雨并引发洪灾，迫使2000余人离开家园，城内积水比海平面还高305毫米<ref name="post1">{{cite news | title = New hurricane whirls in Gulf | agency = United Press Inc. | date = 1979-09-17 | newspaper = The Post-Standard}}</ref>。墨西哥全国范围的最高降雨量达498毫米<ref>{{cite web | author = David M. Roth | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/henri1979filledrainblk.gif | title = Hurricane Henri Color-Filled Rainfall Image | accessdate = 2017-01-26 | work = Weather Prediction Center | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304070331/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/henri1979filledrainblk.gif | format = GIF}}</ref>。

亨利的残留在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]中西部产生降水和[[雷暴|雷暴]]，导致河水泛滥，部分人员疏散<ref name="syracuse2">{{cite news | title = Nation says farewell to summer | agency = United Press Inc. | date = 1979-09-24 | newspaper = Syracuse Herald-Journal}}</ref>。

